INSTALL ($Id: INSTALL,v 1.1.1.1 2000/09/26 19:08:06 plundis Exp $)
=======

Do like this:

1) If you want to change the autochaos.rules files, you need to copy
autochaos/autochaos to somewhere in your PATH (or even better, add the
autochaos directory to your PATH). Otherwise, skip right to the next step.

2) make install

This will copy everything to /mnt/chaos. For more information about
setting things up, see the 'Installation manual' which can be found on
our web page and in the documentation subdirectory.

-- Per Lundberg <plundis@chaosdev.org>  Sun,  6 Aug 2000 15:20:30 +0200